{"search_data": "BiharBihar Mukhyamantri Ati Pichda Varg Udyami Yojana (CM EBC Entrepreneurship Scheme) 2020Bihar govt. starts Mukhyamantri Ati Pichda Varg Udyami Yojana 2020 for extremely backward classes youth, CM EBC Entrepreneurship Scheme to enable jobless candidates to start their own business or setup an enterprise, create self employment & provide job opportunities to other unemployed personsTable of Contents  Bihar Mukhyamantri Ati Pichda Varg Udyami Yojana 2020Bihar Chief Minister\u2019s Extremely Backward Classes Entrepreneurship Scheme BeneficiariesBihar CM EBC Entrepreneurship Scheme 2020 BenefitsBihar Mukhyamantri Ati Pichda Varg Udyami Yojana 2020Here are the important features and highlights of the scheme:-Name of SchemeMukhyamantri Ati Pichda Varg Udyami Yojana or Chief Minister Extremely Backward Classes Entrepreneurship SchemeLaunched ByCM Nitish KumarBeneficiariesYouths belonging to Extremely Backward Class (EBC) categoryObjectiveTo enable EBC youths to start new business or setup an enterpriseFinancial AssistanceRs. 10 lakh in 2 components1st ComponentRs. 5 lakh as state government subsidy2nd ComponentRs. 5 lakh as Interest Free LoansState NameBiharThis information is given by CM Nitish Kumar while addressing programme organized to remember former Bihar CM Karpoori Thakur (Veteran Socialist, EBC Leader) on his birth anniversary. The event was organized by JDU\u2019s EBC Cell at Shri Krishna Memorial Hall in Patna.Bihar Chief Minister\u2019s Extremely Backward Classes Entrepreneurship Scheme BeneficiariesThe state govt. of Bihar will also make arrangement for proper training of selected applicants in their chosen field / project before giving financial assistance. Several castes of Muslim minority community also comes under EBC category. In Bihar state, around 130 castes are listed under the state govt\u2019s EBC category. Out of these, around 36 castes including Ansari, Julaha, Momin, Dhunia, Churihaar, Bakkho, Rangrej, Madar etc comes from Muslim community.Bihar CM EBC Entrepreneurship Scheme 2020 BenefitsCM EBC Entrepreneurship Scheme will come into force from the current financial year after getting approval from the Bihar state cabinet. The new scheme will bring unprecedented socio-economic change among the members of EBCs because majority of castes under this category are either artisans or having traditional entrepreneurship. The assistance of Rs 10 lakh will endure their economic upliftment.Industries department has already prepared a proposal and it would be sent to cabinet secetariat department for putting up in the next cabinet meeting. Besides the state govt. of Bihar has also provided reservation to the members of EBCs in the three-tier Panchayati Raj Institutions to ensure socio-political upliftment of backward classes.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/patna/bihar-nitish-announces-financial-assistance-of-rs-10-lakh-to-extremely-backward-classes-youths/articleshow/73592749.cms  at  "}